{
  "stem": "23572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was two, two prominent papers, which you really didn't  have to buy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could read them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was the-- called the which was the Nazi-- the, the-- was the, the organ of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other one was was the-- it was nothing else to-- it was a pornographic, anti-Semitic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] journal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the guy-- the guy who was the editor on this, a fellow by the name of Julius Streicher, he was hanged in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- S-- S-T-R-E-I-C-H-E-R.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- from what I-- when I read, I started to read-- when I read William Shirer, he was a real obnoxious character to begin with.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was doing nothing else but Jew-baiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so these papers were prominently displayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, you know, if anything was going on-- his paper was, was half-truth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like-- how should I say this-- like, like the to a certain degree, but really, nothing else but anti-Semitic things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Showing a-- showing what Jews do-- that they poison wells and rape German women, [LAUGHS] and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, really, in those days, I really didn't understand quite what that meant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but the was the-- that organ of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anything goes on, you just had to read it-- look at it and read it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it'd tell you what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, then you had the radio, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody had a radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had, had a radio in your house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "TV was not invented yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to watch your step.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you had to know who you're talking to, and what you're saying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You, you had to be-- you had to be alert and be on the ball.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
